title: Jon Gruden, Rodgers-Brady, Browns, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Jon Gruden, Rodgers-Brady, Browns, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses the continued failure of Oakland Raiders HC Jon Gruden, the Aaron Rodgers-Tom Brady match up this weekend, why the Cleveland Browns should've listened to former HC Hue Jackson, and the Blazing 5. Guests include Greg Jennings, Peter King, T. J. Houshmandzadeh, and Rob Parker.
